original_title: Vegetable prices skyrocket in Sri Lanka
original_body_lines: COLOMBO (News 1st) –  Vegetable prices in Sri Lanka skyrocketed on Tuesday (16) to unexpected levels.
These prices were confirmed by the All Ceylon Economic Center Trader's Association
